      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Advanced: Those Crowned Apex",
        "Client": "Rowdy Showman",
        "Description": "Gather \u0027round, gather \u0027round!\r\nTonight we have a grand show\r\nof magnitude and might! Apexes\r\ngalore for your viewing pleasure!\r\nMizutsune! Rathalos! Zinogre!\r\nWho will step up to the challenge!?\r\nCome one \u0027n\u0027 all to find out!",
        "Target": "Slay all target monsters",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Avanc\u00E9 : Sup\u00E9rieurs royaux",
        "Client": "Homme de spectacle",
        "Description": "Approchez, approchez ! Un combat\r\ntitanesque vous attend ce soir !\r\nAdmirez la puissance d\u0027un Mizutsune,\r\nd\u0027un Rathalos et d\u0027un Zinogre...\r\nSUP\u00C9RIEURS ! Il y a-t-il des\r\nvolontaires pr\u00EAts \u00E0 les affronter ?",
        "Target": "Tuer tous les monstres",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Avanzata: Gli Apex coronati",
        "Client": "Showman chiassoso",
        "Description": "Attenzione! Attenzione! Questa\r\nsera si terr\u00E0 uno spettacolo\r\ngrandioso, pieno di Apex che\r\nvi incanteranno: un Mizutsune,\r\nun Rathalos e uno Zinogre! Chi\r\ndecider\u00E0 di affrontare questa\r\nsfida? Venite e lo scoprirete!",
        "Target": "Uccidi tutti i mostri assegnati",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Schwer: Das Apex-Trio",
        "Client": "R\u00FCpelhafter Schausteller",
        "Description": "Menschen, Tiere, Sensationen!\r\nHeute haben wir eine grandiose\r\nVorf\u00FChrung der Extraklasse!\r\nApexe in voller Gr\u00F6\u00DFe und St\u00E4rke!\r\nMizutsune! Rathalos! Zinogre! Wer\r\nstellt sich der Herausforderung?\r\nKommt und findet\u0027s raus!",
